2. **Join Communities:** Participate in forums like Stack Overflow, Reddit’s r/learnprogramming, or local meetups.
3. **Build Projects:** Work on small projects to apply what you’ve learned and gain practical experience.
4. **Read Documentation:** Familiarize yourself with the [Java Documentation](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/index.html).

Happy coding!
